data.description: Join us for Open House this Saturday 10a-12p & Sunday 2p - 4p! This magnificent all-brick residence boasts five bedrooms and three full baths, providing ample space for comfortable living and gracious entertaining. One of the secondary bedrooms has it's own bathroom and outside entrance, perfect for a home based business or in-law suite. Situated on a sprawling lot, this property offers the luxury of expansive outdoor areas, perfect for enjoying the Georgia sunshine and hosting gatherings with friends and family. The five bedrooms offer plenty of room for relaxation and privacy, with the master suite serving as a serene retreat complete with a luxurious ensuite bath and generous walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms are versatile spaces that can accommodate guests, children, or home offices, ensuring everyone has their own comfortable sanctuary. Outside, the expansive lot provides endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, whether it's gardening, playing sports, or simply lounging in the shade of mature trees. The property's excellent location offers convenient access to local amenities, schools, and major transportation routes, making it the perfect combination of luxury and practicality. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional home in Kathleen, where elegant living meets Southern charm in a truly idyllic setting.
